      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "15861-15870",
      "markText": "过后不久，他死了。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30943986&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=15861&rangeEnd=15870",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ad9321d071d82af2ad98b41?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=15861&rangeEnd=15870"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30943986_9_1541-1583",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1541-1583",
      "markText": "但舅舅们背地里谈起“小茨冈”也是气愤的，嘲笑的，他们贬低他的工作，骂他是小偷和懒汉。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30943986&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1541&rangeEnd=1583",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ad9321d071d82af2ad98b41?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1541&rangeEnd=1583"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30943986_10_4758-4798",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "4758-4798",
      "markText": "“他不是劲儿大，是岁数大！再说，他是我的丈夫！上帝叫他管我，我命定该忍受的……”",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30943986&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4758&rangeEnd=4798",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ad9321d071d82af2ad98b41?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4758&rangeEnd=4798"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30943986_19_17958-18081",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "17958-18081",
      "markText": "埋过母亲几天以后，外祖父对我说： “喂，列克谢，你不是一枚奖章，我脖子上不是挂你的地方，你到人间混饭吃去吧……” 于是我就到人间去了。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30943986&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=17958&rangeEnd=18081",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ad9321d071d82af2ad98b41?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=17958&rangeEnd=18081"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30943986_6_4759-4799",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4759-4799",
      "markText": "刚生下来的小弟弟马克西姆死了，包着白布，外面缠着红带子，躺在角落里的一张桌子上。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30943986&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4759&rangeEnd=4799",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ad9321d071d82af2ad98b41?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4759&rangeEnd=4799"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30943986_13_3276-3338",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "3276-3338",
      "markText": "切掉猫尾巴，把狗给毒死，打死公鸡和母鸡，或者半夜偷偷地进到仇人的地窖里，把煤油倒入腌白菜和黄瓜的木桶里，把桶里的克瓦斯放出来",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30943986&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3276&rangeEnd=3338",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ad9321d071d82af2ad98b41?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3276&rangeEnd=3338"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30943986_15_604-702",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "604-702",
      "markText": "小的时候，我想象自己是一个蜂窝，各式各样普通的粗人，全像蜜蜂似的把蜜——生活的知识和思想，送进蜂窝里，他们尽自己所能做到的慷慨大量地丰富我的心灵。这种蜂蜜常常是肮脏而味苦的，但只要是知识，就是蜜。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30943986&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=604&rangeEnd=702",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ad9321d071d82af2ad98b41?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=604&rangeEnd=702"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30943986_18_24327-24407",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "24327-24407",
      "markText": "值得，因为这是一种富有生命力的丑恶的真实，它直到今天还没有消灭。这是一种要想从人的记忆、从灵魂、从我们一切沉重的可耻的生活中连根儿拔掉，就必须从根儿了解的真实。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30943986&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=24327&rangeEnd=24407",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ad9321d071d82af2ad98b41?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=24327&rangeEnd=24407"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30943986_8_11881-11952",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "11881-11952",
      "markText": "从那时起，我怀着不安的心情观察人们，仿佛我心上的外皮给人撕掉了，于是，这颗心就变得对于一切屈辱和痛苦，不论是自己的或别人的，都难以忍受地敏感。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30943986&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11881&rangeEnd=11952",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ad9321d071d82af2ad98b41?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11881&rangeEnd=11952"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30943986_13_14690-14785",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "14690-14785",
      "markText": "家里有许多有趣的和好玩的事，但是有时候，一种无法排遣的愁苦压抑着我，我全身仿佛被一种沉重的东西注满了，好像长久地住在黑暗的深坑里，失去了视觉、听觉和一切感觉，像一个瞎子，一个半死不活的人……",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30943986&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=14690&rangeEnd=14785",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ad9321d071d82af2ad98b41?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=14690&rangeEnd=14785"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30943986_5_1698-1752",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1698-1752",
      "markText": "但是，阿廖沙并没有被这种黑暗的丑事和腐蚀人的恶势力所压倒、所毁灭，反而使他锻炼成了一个坚强、勇敢、正直的人。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30943986&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1698&rangeEnd=1752",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ad9321d071d82af2ad98b41?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1698&rangeEnd=1752"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30943986_8_7799-7846",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "7799-7846",
      "markText": "她善于说这样简短的语句，就好像这些语句把人们从她身边推开，把他们甩得远远的，使他们变得很渺小。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30943986&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7799&rangeEnd=7846",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ad9321d071d82af2ad98b41?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7799&rangeEnd=7846"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30943986_9_20309-20329",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "20309-20329",
      "markText": "“小茨冈”无声无臭地、被人遗忘地埋掉了。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30943986&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=20309&rangeEnd=20329",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ad9321d071d82af2ad98b41?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=20309&rangeEnd=20329"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30943986_6_7331-7372",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7331-7372",
      "markText": "她的头发多得出奇，密密地盖着两肩、胸脯、两膝，一直垂到地上，乌黑乌黑的，泛着蓝光。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30943986&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7331&rangeEnd=7372",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ad9321d071d82af2ad98b41?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7331&rangeEnd=7372"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30943986_9_19745-19783",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "19745-19783",
      "markText": "“混蛋！你们把一个多么能干的小伙子给糟蹋了！再过五六年，他就是无价之宝……”",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30943986&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=19745&rangeEnd=19783",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ad9321d071d82af2ad98b41?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=19745&rangeEnd=19783"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30943986_4_730-798",
